Templates

Advanced editor to create templates and pages using blocks with full control of the design. You can create your own blocks or templates, copy and paste thru different templates.

whoobe creates web static pages with the code that you really need. No bundles.

Thank you to partial hydration of javascript code and CSS optimization based on TailwindCSS, your pages will always be fast and score unique performances.

Templates are the core of whoobe idea and are based on the block paradigma.

Any element created in whoobe is a block, a JSON representation of HTML elements

You can create as many templates as you want, organize in your local filesystem, even export as JSON and import in another whoobe installation.

You design

whoobeOne builds

Serve what you really need

whoobe creates web static pages with the code (javascript, html and CSS) that you really need. No bundles.

Thank you to partial hydration of javascript code, CSS optimization based on TailwindCSS, your pages will always be fast and score unique performances.

No code design

With whoobe editor you can create components, templates and pages without coding but with full control of the design and layout.

Realtime preview and web page creation are included.
